1021
01:08:16,215 --> 01:08:18,365
<i>All right, let's saddle up.</i>

1022
01:08:19,215 --> 01:08:21,171
<i>Let's go! Let's saddle up!</i>

1023
01:08:21,415 --> 01:08:22,928
<i>Let's go, goddamn it!</i>

1024
01:08:26,735 --> 01:08:28,327
