1025
01:08:28,535 --> 01:08:30,924
Good job, Paxton. Good job.

1026
01:08:31,175 --> 01:08:32,733
Good job, Johnson.

1027
01:08:32,935 --> 01:08:33,924
All right.

1028
01:08:34,175 --> 01:08:36,006
Get your ass behind that tree!

1029
01:08:36,215 --> 01:08:39,924
Fantastic. You guys move
like fucking soldiers!

1030
01:08:40,415 --> 01:08:42,326
Get your ass down!

1031
01:08:43,375 --> 01:08:44,933
Ryan, get your ass down!

