1039
01:09:00,695 --> 01:09:02,447
Adapt! Overcome!

1040
01:09:02,695 --> 01:09:04,287
Move! Get in there!

1041
01:09:05,615 --> 01:09:06,604
You good?

1042
01:09:06,855 --> 01:09:08,573
Why were you slow, Paxton?

1043
01:09:08,815 --> 01:09:11,534
- Are you hurt?
- No, I'm fine, sergeant.

1044
01:09:22,295 --> 01:09:23,933
Diagonal, Private Barnes.

1045
01:09:24,175 --> 01:09:27,008
- So you don't chop your knee off.
- Yes, sergeant.

1046
01:09:32,335 --> 01:09:35,133
Go ahead, Paxton.
I gotta take a piss.

1047
01:09:36,175 --> 01:09:37,927
- You okay?
