1050
01:10:43,015 --> 01:10:46,007
You might as well
hang a big neon sign that says:

1051
01:10:46,255 --> 01:10:48,325
"Dumb-fuck grunts, right here."

1052
01:10:48,535 --> 01:10:51,333
You broke light discipline.
