1053
01:10:51,575 --> 01:10:53,531
- Do you understand that?
- Yes, sir.

1054
01:10:53,735 --> 01:10:56,533
- Good.
- I'm still alive, sergeant.

1055
01:10:56,895 --> 01:10:59,932
- What did you say?
- I said, I'm still alive.

1056
01:11:00,415 --> 01:11:03,327
I miraculously survived the attack.

1057
01:11:03,695 --> 01:11:05,526
- You didn't get hit?
- No.

1058
01:11:05,735 --> 01:11:07,054
Are your friends alive?

1059
01:11:07,295 --> 01:11:10,128
Yeah, Paxton's good.
Johnson, he's good and he's good.

1060
01:11:10,455 --> 01:11:13,765
If you're gonna make up a story,
make up a happy one.

1061
01:11:14,575 --> 01:11:16,725
