a few days. We was green as grass.

1067
01:11:47,375 --> 01:11:51,334
We were in a two-man listening post,
talking just like we are here.

1068
01:11:51,975 --> 01:11:54,125
Kelly lit up a cigarette.

1069
01:11:54,975 --> 01:11:57,569
One minute we're naming
his unborn child...

1070
01:11:57,815 --> 01:12:01,285
...and the next second
his brains were in my lap.

1071
01:12:12,895 --> 01:12:16,365
The sniper zeroed in
on the cherry of his cigarette, Bozz.

1072
01:12:20,815 --> 01:12:24,330
Gentlemen, it's all about respect.

1073
01:12:25,415 --> 01:12:28,930
Respect for your superiors
and what they're trying to teach you.

1074
01:12:30,175 --> 01:12:33,326
Respect for yourselves and your unit.

1075
01:12:34,975 --> 01:12:36,931
And most important...

1076
01:12:38,375 --> 01:12:40,127
...respect the enemy.

1077
01:12:45,575 --> 01:12:47,725
You have 42 minutes...

1078
01:12:47,975 --> 01:12:50,535
...then the squad's on patrol.

1079
01:13:03,535 --> 01:13:07,733
Gentlemen, this is the best Vietnamese
village we could create for you...

1080
01:13:07,975 --> 01:13:09,169
...here on the base!

1081
01:13:09,415 --> 01:13:13,249
Now, listen. You're all gooks,
so nobody speaks English.

1082
01:13:13,495 --> 01:13:17,044
Anybody asks you a question
in English, you answer, "No bic."

1083
01:13:17,295 --> 01:13:20,731
It means, "I don't speak" in gook-ese.
Let's hear it.

1084
01:13:21,095 --> 01:13:24,565
Good. Private Bozz, you are
the only man that speaks English.

1085
01:13:24,815 --> 01:13:29,650
Speak only to the man who identifies
himself as interpreter. Understood?

1086
01:13:29,855 --> 01:13:31,573
- Yes, sir.
- Good. Private Paxton.

1087
01:13:31,815 --> 01:13:33,248
You are the Vietcong.

1088
01:13:33,495 --> 01:13:37,932
They come through, their objective
is to find the VC sympathizer.

1089
01:13:38,135 --> 01:13:40,569
In other words, you, Private Paxton.

1090
01:13:40,815 --> 01:13:42,726
They have five minutes.

1091
01:13:42,935 --> 01:13:45,927
You tell them nothing.

1092
01:13:46,415 --> 01:13:47,973
I warn you, they're beat up.

1093
01:13:48,215 --> 01:13:50,046
They've been awake three nights.

1094
01:13:50,295 --> 01:13:51,774
<i>Forced marched all day.</i>

1095
01:13:52,015 --> 01:13:55,974
<i>They fuck this up,</i>
<i>they'll march another six miles.</i>

1096
01:13:56,175 --> 01:13:57,369
<i>One other thing:</i>

1097
01:13:57,615 --> 01:14:01,324
<i>They find out</i>
<i>which one of you is VC...</i>

1098
01:14:01,575 --> 01:14:04,135
<i>... and you'll be the ones</i>
<i>out in the boonies...</i>

1099
01:14:04,335 --> 01:14:07,611
<i>... on no sleep, forced marching</i>
<i>for the next two nights.</i>

1100
01:14:07,815 --> 01:14:08,804
<i>Understood?</i>

1101
01:14:09,055 --> 01:14:10,966
- Yes, sergeant.
- Let's get to work.

1102
01:14:11,215 --> 01:14:13,775
Private Bozz, Paxton. Over here.

1103
01:14:14,015 --> 01:14:17,371
Lets see...
Lukins, Barnes, in this hooch.

1104
01:14:17,615 --> 01:14:19,731
Make it as realistic as possible.

1105
01:14:19,935 --> 01:14:22,130
This is not a fucking joke.

1106
01:14:22,415 --> 01:14:24,770
I like this.
It's like a war theme park.

1107
01:14:25,015 --> 01:14:27,575
I'm so tired. I'm gonna pass out.

1108
01:14:38,535 --> 01:14:40,127
Hey, here they come.

1109
01:14:45,375 --> 01:14:46,728
Shit.

1110
01:14:46,975 --> 01:14:48,169
It's Wilson.

1111
01:14:49,295 --> 01:14:50,523
What?

1112
01:14:50,735 --> 01:14:54,205
- I thought we got him out.
- There's a war going on.

1113
01:14:54,415 --> 01:14:56,724
Plenty of room
for psychopathic killers.

1114
01:14:56,935 --> 01:14:59,403
Let's move it.
We don't got much time.

1115
01:14:59,655 --> 01:15:01,930
We gotta find the VC.

1116
01:15:07,135 --> 01:15:08,727
Fuck me.

1117
01:15:10,615 --> 01:15:11,843
VC?

1118
01:15:13,415 --> 01:15:15,531
Get your ass on the ground!

1119
01:15:19,735 --> 01:15:21,532
Get on the fucking ground!

1120
01:15:22,095 --> 01:15:23,528
You VC?

1121
01:15:24,575 --> 01:15:25,928
You VC?

1122
01:15:27,455 --> 01:15:28,524
How'd that feel?

1123
01:15:28,775 --> 01:15:32,927
Need an interpreter?
I'm the only one that speaks English.

1124
01:15:35,815 --> 01:15:37,487
How does that feel, Paxton?

1125
01:15:43,695 --> 01:15:45,731
What are you gonna write about now?

1126
01:15:50,095 --> 01:15:52,211
What are you writing in your journal?

1127
01:15:58,055 --> 01:15:59,374
Don't fucking move!

1128
01:16:01,215 --> 01:16:03,524
Let go of him, goddamn it!

1129
01:16:10,015 --> 01:16:13,325
- You're in charge! On your feet!
- Yes, sergeant.

1130
01:16:13,815 --> 01:16:16,045
Where is your weapon, soldier?

1131
01:16:16,295 --> 01:16:17,523
There it is.

1132
01:16:17,775 --> 01:16:20,926
Why didn't you secure the area,
Private Wilson?

1133
01:16:21,415 --> 01:16:24,851
I'll tell you why.
Because you lost control!

1134
01:16:25,095 --> 01:16:26,528
Yes, sergeant.

1135
01:16:27,535 --> 01:16:29,765
Did you find any VC?

1136
01:16:30,015 --> 01:16:33,724
No, you didn't.
That's the fucking answer.

1137
01:16:34,095 --> 01:16:35,323
Come here.

1138
01:16:37,255 --> 01:16:41,373
I promise you tears before breakfast.
Get your men and get out of here.

1139
01:16:41,575 --> 01:16:43,725
Get out of here! Let's go. Move!

1140
01:16:43,935 --> 01:16:46,051
- I'm gonna kill you.
- Is that right?

1141
01:16:46,975 --> 01:16:49,170
- You gonna kill me again?
- I'll kill you.

1142
01:16:49,495 --> 01:16:51,247
Get your hands off him!

1143
01:16:52,695 --> 01:16:54,253
You want to go?

1144
01:16:54,495 --> 01:16:56,963
Get the fuck out of here!

1145
01:17:00,895 --> 01:17:03,125
- Get the fuck out!
- I'll break your neck!

1146
01:17:03,495 --> 01:17:05,804
- Let's move!
- Get the fuck out of here!

1147
01:17:06,055 --> 01:17:07,647
